The Bank of England said it has forecasta shortage of around 700 mln stg in the system today.    Among the main factors, maturing assistance and take-up oftreasury bills will drain 546 mln stg, bills for repurchase bythe market 76 mln, a rise in note circulation 310 mln andbankers balances below target 105 mln.    The outflow will be partly offset by 340 mln stg exchequertransactions. REUTER&#3;